text: Aoife O'Rourke (born 2 July 1997) is an Irish amateur boxer. She won the gold medal in the middleweight division at the 2019 Women's European Amateur Boxing Championships. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1997 births Category:Irish women boxers Category:Middleweight boxers Category:Sportspeople from County Roscommon Category:European Games competitors for Ireland Category:Boxers at the 2019 European Games
